# Tutorial: Advanced - Step 8: Git Worktrees
# Shows: Craft git worktree integration

Output advanced-02-worktrees.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 900
Set Height 550
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 15
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

# Title
Type "# Advanced: Git Worktrees with Craft"
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Explain the concept
Type "# Work on multiple branches simultaneously"
Enter
Sleep 1.5s

# Show worktree commands (simulated)
Type "# /craft:git:worktree setup     <- one-time setup"
Enter
Sleep 1.5s

Type "# /craft:git:worktree create feature/new"
Enter
Sleep 1.5s

Type "# /craft:git:worktree list      <- show all"
Enter
Sleep 1.5s

Type "# /craft:git:worktree finish    <- complete feature"
Enter
Sleep 1.5s

# Show native git worktree
Type "git worktree list"
Enter
Sleep 3s
